 \"from\": 3274, \"to\": 3277}, {\"ngram\": \"her much older peers\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To see her compete against 18 year olds is surprising, but that's the age bracket she's in, and she gets better each day.\\\"\", \"from\": 3306, \"to\": 3429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"18 year olds\", \"from\": 3334, \"to\": 3346}, {\"ngram\": \"the age bracket\", \"from\": 3373, \"to\": 3388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Amid the lack of opportunity to train in the Philippines, the POC is throwing its full support to the three.\", \"from\": 3431, \"to\": 3539, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3476, \"end\": 3487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9999954306231107, \"rank\": 4.523969899033402e-06, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 3493, \"end\": 3496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippine_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6549276466528322e-20, \"text\": \"POC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippine_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippine_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lack\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3444}, {\"ngram\": \"opportunity\", \"from\": 3448, \"to\": 3459}, {\"ngram\": \"its full support\", \"from\": 3509, \"to\": 3525}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Philippines may be a tropical country, but the Olympic spirit knows no boundaries,\\\" said Tolentino.\", \"from\": 3541, \"to\": 3645, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3546, \"end\": 3557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9999954306231107, \"rank\": 4.523969899033402e-06, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\